toli cells via P/Q type voltage-operated calcium channels [Barone et al., 2005].  The p.o. administration of ethylene glycol monomethyl (500 mg/kg/day) in rats induced the testis or liver organ weight loss on 2, 4, 7, and 11 days or 24 hrs and 2, 4, and 7 days after treatment, respectively [Foster et al., 1983].  The investigation of 2-methoxyethanol (2-ME)-induced testicular toxicity has revealed that the conversion of 2-ME to MAA is required in 2-ME-induced testicular toxicity [Moss et al., 1985].", "timestamp": "Mon Jun 08 15:01:22 +0000 2026"}